<i>adverb</i>: 훤히 [훤ː히], 환히 [환ː히], 확연히 [화견히], 완연히 [와ː년히], 역력히 [영녀키], 뻔히 [뻔ː히], 빤히 [빤ː히], 번연히 [번연히], 명확히 [명화키], 명료히 [명뇨히], 단연히 [다ː년히], 단연코 [다ː년코], 단연 [다ː년], 극명히 [긍명히] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>훤히 [훤ː히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. brightly; lightly</dd><br>
<dd>조금 흐릿할 정도로 밝게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being slightly, dimly bright.</dd><br>
<dd>2. openly; clearly</dd><br>
<dd>앞이 탁 트여 매우 넓고 시원스럽게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of view being sweeping and unobstructed.</dd><br>
<dd>3. clearly; obviously</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일의 내용이나 사정이 확실하고 분명하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of something being transparent, obvious or quite predictable.</dd><br>
<dd>4. attractively; finely; handsomely</dd><br>
<dd>외모가 잘생겨 보기에 매우 시원스럽게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of having an extremely pleasing, neat, attractive appearance.</dd><br>
<dd>5. clearly; exactly; well</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일이나 대상에 대해 잘 알고 있는 상태로.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of having an accurate and deep knowledge about a certain task or object.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>환히 [환ː히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. brightly; radiantly</dd><br>
<dd>빛이 비치어 맑고 밝게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being very clear and bright as light shines.</dd><br>
<dd>2. openly; clearly</dd><br>
<dd>앞이 탁 트여 넓고 시원스럽게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of something imparting a feeling of not being confined, because it has an open view.</dd><br>
<dd>3. clearly; obviously</dd><br>
<dd>무슨 일이 되어 가는 사정이나 속내가 분명하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of the progress or intention of a certain event being clear.</dd><br>
<dd>4. attractively; finely; neatly</dd><br>
<dd>얼굴이 깔끔하게 잘생겨 보기에 좋게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of having a pleasing, neat, and attractive appearance.</dd><br>
<dd>5. brightly; beamingly; radiantly</dd><br>
<dd>표정이나 성격이 명랑하고 밝게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of one's face or personality being bright and cheerful.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>확연히 [화견히]</dt><br>
<dd>clearly; definitely; obviously</dd><br>
<dd>아주 확실하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Very clearly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>완연히 [와ː년히]</dt><br>
<dd>obviously; evidently</dd><br>
<dd>눈에 보이는 것처럼 아주 뚜렷하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a very clear manner as if one could see something right before one's eyes.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>역력히 [영녀키]</dt><br>
<dd>clearly; obviously</dd><br>
<dd>감정이나 모습, 기억 등이 또렷하고 분명하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of one's feelings, appearance, memory, etc., being distinct and definite.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>뻔히 [뻔ː히]</dt><br>
<dd>obviously</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일의 결과나 상태 등이 눈에 보이듯 분명하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner that the result, state, etc., of something is seen clearly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>빤히 [빤ː히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. brightly</dd><br>
<dd>어둠 속에서 밝은 빛이 비치어 환하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being slightly bright as a light shines in darkness.</dd><br>
<dd>2. plainly; obviously</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일의 결과나 상태가 분명하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which the result or state of something is clear.</dd><br>
<dd>3. fixedly; steadily; intently</dd><br>
<dd>바라보는 것이 정면으로 또렷하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of one's staring eyes being clear.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>번연히 [번연히]</dt><br>
<dd>obviously</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일의 결과나 상태 등이 훤하게 들여다보이듯이 분명하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that the result, state, etc., of something is seen clearly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>명확히 [명화키]</dt><br>
<dd>clearly; obviously</dd><br>
<dd>분명하고 확실하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Clearly and surely.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>명료히 [명뇨히]</dt><br>
<dd>clearly; obviously</dd><br>
<dd>분명하고 확실하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Clearly and surely.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>단연히 [다ː년히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. obviously</dd><br>
<dd>순위나 수준, 정도 등이 확실히 판단이 될 만큼 뚜렷하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Obviously in deciding a rank, level, degree, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>2. surely</dd><br>
<dd>흔들리거나 망설이지 않고.</dd><br>
<dd>Without being shaken or hesitating.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>단연코 [다ː년코]</dt><br>
<dd>1. obviously</dd><br>
<dd>순위나 수준, 정도 등이 확실히 판단이 될 만큼 뚜렷하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Obviously in deciding a rank, level, degree, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>2. by all means</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 경우에도 절대로.</dd><br>
<dd>Absolutely in whatever occasion.</dd><br>
<dd>3. surely</dd><br>
<dd>무슨 일이 있어도 꼭.</dd><br>
<dd>Surely, despite anything.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>단연 [다ː년]</dt><br>
<dd>obviously</dd><br>
<dd>무엇의 순위나 수준, 정도 등이 확실히 판단이 될 만큼 뚜렷하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Obviously in deciding the rank, level, degree, etc., of something.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>극명히 [긍명히]</dt><br>
<dd>definitely; obviously; distinctly</dd><br>
<dd>매우 분명하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Very clearly.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>